{
  "texts": [
    "In the present section, I introduce the main concepts for my argument.",
    "I will develop the following Kantian dichotomy.",
    "On the one hand, there are mechanistic artifacts, which fulfill a purpose specified from the outside.",
    "They function or malfunction according to the specifications given to them.",
    "It makes no sense to distinguish a malfunctioning of such a thing from a willful act of deceit or disobedience."
  ]
}